{"tid":1432801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完民間記者會同撚狗嘉年華，點解無下一步實質行動?","createTime":"2019-08-08T10:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:47:19.000Z","uid":302215,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f405fa1536014a2ffe8d79877debf7d30230f7e5","tid":1432801,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"今日的第二次民間記者會真係好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再睇埋狗隻記招一如以往被記者撚狗咁撚，大家係咪覺得好爽今日好成功呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌！成件事未完架，可唔可以唔好浪費民間記者會的成果?</span></strong></span> 地鐵仲係咁聽到d廢佬仲係度鐳射傷人乜乜乜，全部入晒我哋數。記者會嘅嘢仲未散到出去呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">我地要全民文宣呀，想當日的放映會呢? 傳單呢? </span></span>我行到返屋企路過地鐵站連儂牆都見唔到有人做。大家邊個有時間得閒，或者放咗工就落去幫下手啦！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">單靠民間記者會而冇其他行動support，只會死路一條。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n警世！仲有無人記得當年各區派傳單同放映會盛況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431353</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便一推，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>明天9/8香港機場和你飛</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府越係不要不要你做的事，就證明你做的事越正確。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［突發］和你飛 集會無人呀！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sp6cdd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsp6cdd5.jpg&h=5fc814a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda64b889fca2c7566e6f4cc61be248812a28d88","tid":1432801,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"警察記者會真係好成功<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1432746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1432746</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3fb143acb5e32adcfc142e3e8a9c86599d6a02b0","tid":1432801,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"聽日機場見"},{"pid":"4c77ed6bb7ce49d64c61d69909c7c6d5ff10110d","tid":1432801,"uid":251292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"唔係撚狗「嘉年華」<br />\n今日見到啲人開始po「江sir飲水」啲post<br />\n有啲似以前4點鐘許sir咩recap in English<br />\n千其唔好膠化個記者會<br />\n因為呢個係每日狙擊佢地既好時機"},{"pid":"161a4b3bcfb51a00876d419f2711049a8a84c5ce","tid":1432801,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fb143acb5e32adcfc142e3e8a9c86599d6a02b0","tid":1432801,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"聽日機場見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"唔單止機場，民間記者會段片已經出左黎。大家係時候瘋狂放映會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2404346966307573&amp;id=258224170919874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2404346966307573%26id%3D258224170919874&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7wWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=778355c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2404346966307573&amp;id=258224170919874</a>"},{"pid":"33a1c2002e247cf8f4e60263995d067ae7f51946","tid":1432801,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c77ed6bb7ce49d64c61d69909c7c6d5ff10110d","tid":1432801,"uid":251292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score